{"tid":1603484,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動] [長文] 10.1 最新五區革命研究","createTime":"2019-09-29T16:38:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T12:22:08.000Z","uid":69419,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"172af1d4e167f5d3c8ee0fd51b23e70aa35e2531","tid":1603484,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:38:09.000Z","msg":"先睇原post<br />\n10月1日 五區革命<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1585140\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1585140</a><br />\n長話短說, 五個地方, 完成目標就走<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">尖沙咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 封紅隧 <br />\n2. 封高鐵 <br />\n3. 梳士巴利花園立旗宣示港人治港</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">優劣: 九龍西手足副本, 唯一能切斷境外增援既市區, 不過目標相距極遠, 建議一個一個目標進行 </span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黃大仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 封龍翔道<br />\n2. 黃大仙廟廣場立旗宣示港人治港</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>優劣: 九龍東手足副本, 切斷東西九龍交通, 目標相距短甚至可以同時進行, 但要面對來自觀塘既壓力</strong></span><br />\n(P.S.仙人護體)</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">荃灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 破壞二坡坊<br />\n2. 大堂廣場立旗宣示港人治港</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>優劣: 新界西手足副本, 打擊黑社會, 搶佔道德高地</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">沙田<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 佔領新城市廣場<br />\n2. 大會堂廣場立旗宣示港人治港 </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>優劣: 新界東手足副本, 居民協助力強, 目標難度低, 能否維持係關鍵</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">金鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 佔領政總<br />\n2. 添馬公園立旗宣示港人治港 </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>優劣: 港島區手足副本, 最熟悉戰場, 最難副本, 建議已完他區任務手足增援</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">每區時間都係中午12點, 今次唔好遲啦!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">每個區都有額外副本: <br />\n燒當區狗屋, 不過風險極大, 請自行決定</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後, 附上香港旗為結<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3QZYAy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3QZYAy.jpg&h=e54b77c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y3TMDCk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY3TMDCk.jpg&h=b93e108a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a456692824b3e091a15ac3256685fcf38531596","tid":1603484,"uid":69419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:38:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y3TMDCk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY3TMDCk.jpg&h=b93e108a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eed3198c808f1e935c923af67d5886af7aeaf6d2","tid":1603484,"uid":69419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:38:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y3TMDCk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY3TMDCk.jpg&h=b93e108a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5668e332310cf4f3b95c8253236a778f22dad38","tid":1603484,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:39:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2d29f29b6d268cca8c11dea01d881e02afcaae49","tid":1603484,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:40:32.000Z","msg":"你哋每次想打飛機嘅時候，幻想下係有幾隻警犬係你前面，一個幫你舔春袋，一個幫你毒龍鑽，兩個奶你粒lin，應該好快就戒到J。"},{"pid":"be55ca38f1be0319105be452d0b118252e831cae","tid":1603484,"uid":153250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"s